	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡Enhorabuena, flor!<delay20 /> <anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Aquí tienes mi <tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />.<delay20 /> ¡Cuídal<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x12 0xcd00 0x2 0x6f 0x2 0x61 0x0" /> bien!</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Vaya,<delay8 /> he perdido yo,<delay8 /> qué penita.<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />En fin, puedes quedarte mi
